recover() - Method in class org.batfish.grammar.BatfishLexerRecoveryStrategy
Wrap current unmatchable char up to next char in provided separator chars in a BatfishLexer.UNMATCHABLE_TOKEN and emit it.
recoverInCurrentNode(Parser) - Method in class org.batfish.grammar.BatfishANTLRErrorStrategy
